{"tid":1054491,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"嘩屌！2017年HTC機，刷完Oreo好似新旗艦一樣！","createTime":"2019-03-09T23:00:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-12T01:54:17.000Z","uid":202464,"like":2,"dislike":53,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"f7b94126dcf6c28f106a44c3b438494cbcd90b42","tid":1054491,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T23:00:49.000Z","msg":"我都唔係成日換電話/upgrade個OS既人，一黎怕裝過晒d野麻煩；二黎驚好似iphone咁，越升os越部機會越lag，係商家逼你買新機既技倆。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢幾日日日落雨無街去，屎忽痕走去刷oreo。第一次刷可能無清CACHE，刷出黎問題多多，聯絡人唔識SYNC、打電話會彈APP。決定好好地刷多次。出乎意料效果好好，本身NOUGAT都開心使用緊，而家仲開心。有唔少細緻位改善左，<br />\n<br />\nE.G. Login WIFI準確又快左，apps權限又可以自己訂，<br />\n<br />\n不過係d icon核突晒。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nbtw，不嬲root開，為左裝開心版九方（我認我廢，唔識打倉頡），為左裝ad away，為左uninstall bloatware，為左整走app入面既ad（連登&hellip;）<br />\n<br />\n唯一唔好處就係root完裝唔到銀行app同乜七pay。不過無所謂啦，用銀行m版網頁都一樣既je<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />至於乜七pay，我又唔係先進既支那人，用返實體信用卡無問題。"},{"pid":"3b44e8423ca8e701c392b005af29e4af48a5627f","tid":1054491,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T00:25:56.000Z","msg":"樓主刷邊個rom<br />\n<br />\n我有部LG G2, 都想刷rom<br />\n求教學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d81d60863d03daf46380537034b4c584f1c04c6a","tid":1054491,"uid":70183,"like":8,"dislike":8,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T00:54:31.000Z","msg":"原來而家仲有人root機"},{"pid":"6077d1d621afa11b129e49d516ef4ae937bfa2e2","tid":1054491,"uid":202464,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T02:02:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主刷邊個rom<br />\n<br />\n我有部LG G2, 都想刷rom<br />\n求教學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都係去xda搵。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我自己會盡量揀返原廠rom去root。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n間間廠刷rom/root機既方法雖大同小異，但exact既step有唔同。我見議去xda搵你部機既教學穩陣。"},{"pid":"78023300178fc539df93e1f486b3272c2e3f8395","tid":1054491,"uid":202464,"like":4,"dislike":9,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T02:03:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>原來而家仲有人root機</blockquote><br />\n有。我次次都root。無計，<br />\n<br />\n一，我只識打九方<br />\n<br />\n二，我極討厭廣告。所以一定要剷除"},{"pid":"07c42a340d5c59bcb7e1b67613fed5ac788df461","tid":1054491,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T06:02:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49c0f5b546345347e040732ef49c0be79461c3d4","tid":1054491,"uid":105678,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T06:09:25.000Z","msg":"magisk框架可以用銀行app的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f20ffbf74120c8aa9c63524590a2a626d8f41eb2","tid":1054491,"uid":33903,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"d81d60863d03daf46380537034b4c584f1c04c6a","tid":1054491,"uid":70183,"like":8,"dislike":8,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T00:54:31.000Z","msg":"原來而家仲有人root機"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T06:10:34.000Z","msg":"唔root邊得<br />\n<br />\n反正最新果d root<br />\n有方法可以令個app check唔到有root<br />\n咁點解唔root"},{"pid":"a15a45ad1f4fdc31dc89dc1f24b5a746d8d75168","tid":1054491,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T06:33:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>magisk框架可以用銀行app的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係。但唔知點解用magsik既方法出error root唔到。"},{"pid":"74d70c0147b5db0af21d0e6f91f8ae15c1ba54fe","tid":1054491,"uid":100697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T06:54:09.000Z","msg":"聽日要返工啦wo"},{"pid":"1bce2dc2d154d931ffd7342b7d5ed2294e432309","tid":1054491,"uid":36136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T09:15:45.000Z","msg":"咩機？"},{"pid":"d330145b23a3f30ed01ce61c9dbe55b76f211393","tid":1054491,"uid":16904,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T09:44:12.000Z","msg":"用一排咪又係慢...<br />\n部機新出個陣咪又係個個話順<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6375c0